<p>TIL from <a href="https://twitter.com/liamnichols_/status/1018812142693253120?s=12">this tweet</a>, that you can enable showing touches on iOS simulator. This is handy for making nicer screencasts.</p>
<pre><code class="language-{.bash">defaults write http://com.apple .iphonesimulator ShowSingleTouches 1
</code></pre>
